text: Bärbel Jungmeier (born 8 July 1975) is a road cyclist and mountain bike rider from Austria. She represented her nation at the 2004 Summer Olympics in the Women's cross-country.Bärbel Jungmeier sport-reference.com She also competed at the 2006 UCI Road World Championships. ==References== ==External links== * profile at Procyclingstats.com Category:1975 births Category:Austrian female cyclists Category:Living people Category:Sportspeople from Villach Category:Cyclists at the 2004 Summer Olympics Category:Olympic cyclists of Austria
